Author: Gateway#3763
Content:
[telegram] <Acura360> Regarding a question for rebranding, Steve (Chief Marketing Officer) have said below comments:
There is already a pre-launch campaign in plan for the launch. This will only be announced when all deliverables are complete and both Komodo and IBN have agreed we're ready. We haven't ruled out a launch countdown for the site, but that is a minor piece in the overall rebrand project. The current idea is we introduce the new brand in different segment areas: why are we rebranding? Who and what is new Komodo?, new messaging, new logo, visual identity and style guidelines, UX/UI style guides and direction, strategic goals and roadmap update, then site launch. It's been a bit quiet as we're getting ready to launch a new interim website update, and are making final decisions on the rebrand proposals. The only thing we're not committing to yet are dates, until we're further along and can guarantee that those dates won't slip.
